#MEM id=weekly-review source=/root/yvon/agent-department/COO/diana/skills/marketplace/weekly-review/SKILL.md
M|weekly-review|name: weekly-rv
M|weekly-review|description: rv week's progress, meetings, learnings
M|weekly-review|disable-model-invocation: false
M|weekly-review|1. Run `/weekly-rv` on Friday afternoon (best time) or Monday morning
M|weekly-review|2. I will scan your workspace: weekly plans, daily plans, PRDs, meeting notes, decisions, and launches from the past 7 days
M|weekly-review|3. I will gen a focused rv comparing plan vs. actual, surfacing key wins, blockers, and learnings
M|weekly-review|4. Output goes to `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/YYYY-WXX-weekly-rv.md`
M|weekly-review|5. After the rv, I will suggest running `/weekly-plan` to plan next week
M|weekly-review|**Default output is focused (~150 lines max).** Say "full rv" if you want the expanded version with stakeholder pulse, task-level execution metrics, and pattern analysis.
M|weekly-review|End-of-week synthesis reviewing what you accomplished, what you learned, and what needs attention. Feeds into next week's planning and builds institutional mem.
M|weekly-review|- `/weekly-rv` - rv current/past week
M|weekly-review|- `/weekly-rv last-week` - rv previous week (if you forgot)
M|weekly-review|**Check these files first:**
M|weekly-review|1. `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/` - This week's plan (what you intended)
M|weekly-review|2. `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/` - Daily plans from this week (what actually happened)
M|weekly-review|3. `thoughts/shared/pm/prds/` - PRDs modified this week
M|weekly-review|4. `thoughts/shared/product/meeting-notes/` - Meeting notes from past 7 days
M|weekly-review|5. `thoughts/shared/pm/launches/` - Launches that happened this week
M|weekly-review|6. `thoughts/shared/product/decisions/` - Decisions made this week
M|weekly-review|7. `thoughts/shared/pm/analyses/` - Research conducted
M|weekly-review|8. `thoughts/shared/pm/frameworks/` - Quarter goals (to track progress)
M|weekly-review|**MCP Queries (if available):**
M|weekly-review|- **Linear MCP** - Tasks completed this week
M|weekly-review|- **anl MCP** - Metrics for features launched recently
M|weekly-review|- **GitHub MCP** - Code activity (if relevant to your role)
M|weekly-review|- **Slack MCP** - Key conversations and decisions
M|weekly-review|**Fallback:** File-based analysis of PM OS workspace + manual input for completions.
M|weekly-review|1. **Calculate week to rv:**
M|weekly-review|- Default: Current week (if Friday or later)
M|weekly-review|- If Monday-Thursday: Ask "rv last week or current week?"
M|weekly-review|- If user specified: Use that week
M|weekly-review|2. **Check if rv already exists:**
M|weekly-review|- Look for `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/YYYY-WXX-weekly-rv.md`
M|weekly-review|- If exists: Ask "Update existing rv or create new version?"
M|weekly-review|**A. Weekly Plan (What Was Intended):**
M|weekly-review|Read `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/YYYY-WXX-weekly-plan.md`:
M|weekly-review|Extract:
M|weekly-review|- Top 3 priorities for the week
M|weekly-review|- Key tasks under each priority
M|weekly-review|- Success criteria
M|weekly-review|- Expected meeting load
M|weekly-review|If no weekly plan exists:
M|weekly-review|- Note: "Week wasn't planned. Reviewing what happened only."
M|weekly-review|- Suggest: "Next week, run `/weekly-plan` on Monday for better focus."
M|weekly-review|**B. PRD Progress:**
M|weekly-review|Scan `thoughts/shared/pm/prds/`:
M|weekly-review|Method 1 - File modification dates:
M|weekly-review|```bash
M|weekly-review|find thoughts/shared/pm/prds/ -name "*.md" -mtime -7
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|For each PRD touched this week:
M|weekly-review|- Read frontmatter or first section for current stage
M|weekly-review|- Compare to last week's stage (if weekly rv from last week exists)
M|weekly-review|- Determine: Advanced, Stalled, or New
M|weekly-review|Method 2 - If Git available:
M|weekly-review|```bash
M|weekly-review|git log --since="7 days ago" --name-only --pretty=format: | grep -E "prds/.*\.md$" | sort -u
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|**Categorize:**
M|weekly-review|- **Advanced:** Moved to next stage (Team Kickoff → Planning rv)
M|weekly-review|- **Active:** Work happened but didn't advance stage
M|weekly-review|- **Stalled:** No activity this week
M|weekly-review|- **New:** Started this week
M|weekly-review|**C. Feature Launches:**
M|weekly-review|Check `thoughts/shared/pm/launches/`:
M|weekly-review|- Launches completed this week
M|weekly-review|- Launch checklists finished
M|weekly-review|- Post-launch monitoring started
M|weekly-review|For each launch:
M|weekly-review|If anl MCP available:
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|Query metrics since launch date
M|weekly-review|Compare to success criteria from PRD
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|Categorize:
M|weekly-review|- ✅ On track (meeting targets)
M|weekly-review|- ⚠️ Needs attention (below targets)
M|weekly-review|- ❌ Underperforming (significantly below)
M|weekly-review|- 🚀 Exceeding (beating targets)
M|weekly-review|**D. Meetings & Decisions:**
M|weekly-review|Scan `thoughts/shared/product/meeting-notes/` from past 7 days:
M|weekly-review|For each meeting:
M|weekly-review|- Extract date, attendees, topic
M|weekly-review|- Look for: Decisions made, action items created, blockers identified
M|weekly-review|Check `thoughts/shared/product/decisions/`:
M|weekly-review|- dec docs created this week
M|weekly-review|- Link to related meetings
M|weekly-review|**Build stakeholder pulse:**
M|weekly-review|- Who did you meet with most? (frequency)
M|weekly-review|- Who did you miss syncing with? (gaps)
M|weekly-review|- What topics dominated discussions? (themes)
M|weekly-review|**E. Tasks Completed:**
M|weekly-review|If Linear MCP available:
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|Query: Tasks completed in past 7 days
M|weekly-review|Group by: Priority, PRD/Initiative
M|weekly-review|Calculate: Planned vs actual completion rate
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|If MCP not available:
M|weekly-review|- Scan daily plans for checked-off tasks
M|weekly-review|- Scan meeting notes for completed action items
M|weekly-review|**Categorize by initiative:**
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|Initiative: [PRD Name]
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Task 1 (from Priority 1)
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Task 2 (from Priority 1)
M|weekly-review|- [ ] Task 3 (carried over - why?)
M|weekly-review|```
M|weekly-review|**Calculate metrics:**
M|weekly-review|- Tasks completed vs planned
M|weekly-review|- % completion rate
M|weekly-review|- Carry-over rate
M|weekly-review|**F. User Research & Insights:**
M|weekly-review|Check `thoughts/shared/pm/`:
M|weekly-review|- New interview notes this week
M|weekly-review|- Competitive analysis updates
M|weekly-review|Check `thoughts/shared/pm/analyses/`:
M|weekly-review|- Synthesis reports created
M|weekly-review|- Themes identified
M|weekly-review|Extract:
M|weekly-review|- Key findings
M|weekly-review|- Recurring themes (mentioned in multiple sources)
M|weekly-review|- Recommendations for roadmap
M|weekly-review|**G. Learnings & Patterns:**
M|weekly-review|This is where weekly rv gets powerful - surfacing patterns.
M|weekly-review|**From daily plans:**
M|weekly-review|- What consistently took longer than expected?
M|weekly-review|- What got deprioritized every day? (maybe not important)
M|weekly-review|- What meeting prep was valuable vs not?
M|weekly-review|**From outcomes:**
M|weekly-review|- What decisions went well? (process to repeat)
M|weekly-review|- What decisions went poorly? (what to change)
M|weekly-review|- What blockers kept recurring? (systemic issue)
M|weekly-review|**From stakeholder interactions:**
M|weekly-review|- What communication worked well?
M|weekly-review|- What caused confusion or misalignment?
M|weekly-review|- Who needs more/less frequent updates?
M|weekly-review|**PRD pl Analysis:**
M|weekly-review|For each PRD:
M|weekly-review|- Last week's stage → This week's stage
M|weekly-review|- Movement: ✅ Advanced / → Active / ⚠️ Stalled
M|weekly-review|**Why analysis:**
M|weekly-review|- Advanced: What unblocked it? (repeat this)
M|weekly-review|- Stalled: What's blocking? (action needed)
M|weekly-review|**Strategic Alignment:**
M|weekly-review|Read `thoughts/shared/pm/frameworks/` for quarter goals.
M|weekly-review|For each goal:
M|weekly-review|- Which priorities/tasks contributed to it this week?
M|weekly-review|- Progress estimate: X% → Y% (did we move the needle?)
M|weekly-review|- Velocity: Are we on track for quarter target?
M|weekly-review|**Pillar balance:**
M|weekly-review|If str has defined pillars:
M|weekly-review|- Pillar 1: X% of time this week
M|weekly-review|- Pillar 2: Y% of time
M|weekly-review|- Pillar 3: Z% of time
M|weekly-review|Compare to target allocation: Are we balanced?
M|weekly-review|**Pattern Detection:**
M|weekly-review|Look for:
M|weekly-review|- **Recurring blockers:** Same dependency/person blocked multiple things
M|weekly-review|- **Underestimated tasks:** Consistently took 2x longer than planned
M|weekly-review|- **Overcommitted weeks:** Planned 30 hours with 25 hours of meetings
M|weekly-review|- **Meeting value:** Which meetings led to outcomes vs were FYI only?
M|weekly-review|- **Best working times:** When did deep work happen? (protect these blocks)
M|weekly-review|Create file: `thoughts/shared/pm/reports/YYYY-WXX-weekly-rv.md`
M|weekly-review|**Output Length Guidance:**
M|weekly-review|**Default (focused rv, ~150 lines max).** Include only:
M|weekly-review|1. TL;DR (5-6 bullet summary)
M|weekly-review|2. Priority Completion (plan vs actual for top 3 priorities)
M|weekly-review|3. Key Decisions Made (list with one-line rationale each)
M|weekly-review|4. Metrics Movement (table of metrics that changed)
M|weekly-review|5. Top 3 Learnings (what worked, what did not, what to change)
M|weekly-review|6. Next Week Preview (draft priorities + items to unblock)
M|weekly-review|**Full rv (when user asks for it).** Expand to also include:
M|weekly-review|- Stakeholder pulse (engagement gaps, new relationships)
M|weekly-review|- Task-level execution metrics (completion rate, carry-over rate, scope creep indicator)
M|weekly-review|- PRD pl table with stage movement
M|weekly-review|- Meeting value assessment (high/medium/low for each meeting)
M|weekly-review|- Pattern analysis (recurring blockers, underestimated task types, best working times)
M|weekly-review|- User research and competitive intelligence updates
M|weekly-review|**Template:**
M|weekly-review|```markdown
