M|weekly-review|After generating rv, prompt user with contextual suggestions:
M|weekly-review|**Always offer:**
M|weekly-review|> "Week synthesized and saved! Next steps:
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> 1. **Plan next week?** Run `/weekly-plan` (5-10 min) - I've drafted initial priorities above
M|weekly-review|> 2. **Share with team?** I can format this as a stakeholder update
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> What would help?"
M|weekly-review|**If significant wins:**
M|weekly-review|> "🎉 Nice work on [Achievement]! Worth documenting this:
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> - Add to portfolio/resume
M|weekly-review|> - Share in team update
M|weekly-review|> - Capture as case study for future reference
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> Want me to help with any of these?"
M|weekly-review|**If patterns emerged:**
M|weekly-review|> "📊 I noticed some patterns:
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> - [Recurring blocker X] appeared [Y] times
M|weekly-review|> - [Task type Z] consistently took 2x longer than estimated
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> Want to dig into these and create process improvements?"
M|weekly-review|**If learnings captured:**
M|weekly-review|> "💡 This week's learnings worth remembering:
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> - [Learning 1]
M|weekly-review|> - [Learning 2]
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> I'll surface these in future planning. Want me to add to `thoughts/shared/pm/ctx/lessons-learned.md`?"
M|weekly-review|**If metrics concerning:**
M|weekly-review|> "⚠️ [Feature] metrics need attention:
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> - [Metric] is [X%] below target
M|weekly-review|> - Trending [down/flat] since launch
M|weekly-review|>
M|weekly-review|> Run `/feature-results` for deeper analysis? Or schedule stakeholder rv?"
M|weekly-review|**Before `/weekly-rv`:**
M|weekly-review|- `/daily-plan` - Ran throughout the week (provides daily ctx)
M|weekly-review|- `/meeting-notes` - Captured meeting outcomes
M|weekly-review|- `/prd-draft` - Created/updated PRDs this week
M|weekly-review|**After `/weekly-rv`:**
M|weekly-review|- `/weekly-plan` - Plan next week based on this rv
M|weekly-review|- `/dec-doc` - doc key decisions made
M|weekly-review|- `/status-update` - Share with stakeholders
M|weekly-review|- `/feature-results` - Deep dive on launched features
M|weekly-review|**Parallel use:**
M|weekly-review|- `/impact-sizing` - Validate completed work had expected impact
M|weekly-review|- `/cp-analysis` - If competitive intel emerged this week
M|weekly-review|**When to run:**
M|weekly-review|- **Best time:** Friday afternoon (4-5pm)
M|weekly-review|- Week is fresh in mem
M|weekly-review|- Can plan next week immediately after
M|weekly-review|- Creates clean mental closure for weekend
M|weekly-review|- **Alternative:** Monday morning (reflect before planning)
M|weekly-review|- **Avoid:** Mid-week (incomplete picture)
M|weekly-review|**What makes a good rv:**
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Honest about what didn't go well (not just wins)
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Specific about patterns (not vague "work harder")
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Actionable improvements (concrete next steps)
M|weekly-review|- ✅ Connects to str (not just task completion)
M|weekly-review|- ❌ Just a task list (misses the "why" and learnings)
M|weekly-review|- ❌ All problems, no wins (demotivating)
M|weekly-review|**How to build the habit:**
M|weekly-review|- Week 1-2: I'll prompt you Friday afternoon
M|weekly-review|- Week 3-4: You'll start expecting it (ritual forming)
M|weekly-review|- Week 5+: Feels incomplete without it
M|weekly-review|**Use the output:**
M|weekly-review|- Reference in 1:1s with manager (shows progress)
M|weekly-review|- Share with stakeholders (transparency)
M|weekly-review|- Compare month-over-month (velocity trends)
M|weekly-review|- rv quarterly (pattern detection across multiple weeks)
M|weekly-review|**Before this:**
M|weekly-review|- `/daily-plan` - Daily execution throughout week
M|weekly-review|- `/weekly-plan` - Set priorities at start of week
M|weekly-review|- `/meeting-notes` - Captured throughout week
M|weekly-review|**After this:**
M|weekly-review|- `/weekly-plan` - Plan next week immediately after rv
M|weekly-review|- `/status-update` - Share summary with stakeholders
M|weekly-review|- `/dec-doc` - Formalize key decisions made
M|weekly-review|**Periodic use:**
M|weekly-review|- `/feature-results` - Monthly deep dive on launched features
M|weekly-review|- `/quarter-rv` - (If exists) Quarterly synthesis of weekly reviews
M|weekly-review|Before delivering the weekly rv, verify:
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Plan vs. actual compared:** If a weekly plan existed, every planned priority is addressed with a status (complete, partial, not started) and a reason for any gap.
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Learnings are specific and actionable:** Each learning includes what happened, why, and a concrete change for next time. "Work harder" is not a learning.
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Next week priorities are drafted:** At least 3 draft priorities for next week are suggested, grounded in this week's outcomes and strategic goals.
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Blockers have owners:** Every unresolved blocker has a specific action and person to contact on Monday.
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Metrics referenced where available:** If launches happened or metrics data exists, actual numbers are cited (not just "things went well").
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Appropriate length:** Default rv is ~150 lines. Full rv is longer but still organized with clear section headers. Do not gen a full rv unless the user asked for one.
M|weekly-review|- [ ] **Honest about what did not go well:** The rv includes at least one thing that did not go as planned, with root cause analysis. A rv with only wins is incomplete.